message: "If you use this archive, please cite the manuscript and the archived release."
title: "Exact Computer-Assisted Exclusion of the (72,108) Frontier in the Two-Dimensional Jacobian Problem"
type: software
version: 1.0.1
date-released: 2026-07-21
authors:
  - family-names: Helali
    given-names: Billel
abstract: >-
  Exact characteristic-zero certificate replay for the two Laurent/Newton
  coefficient systems associated with the remaining (72,108) degree pair in
  the two-dimensional Jacobian problem. The degree-125 consequence is
  conditional on the correctness and exhaustiveness of the published
  reduction and its faithful transcription.
keywords:
  - Jacobian conjecture
  - computer algebra
  - exact certificate
  - Newton polygon
  - characteristic zero
repository-code: "https://github.com/bilLkarkariy/jc2-72-108-exact-certificates"
